<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <%- include('../partials/head') %>
    <style>
        .success-page {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 8rem 2rem 4rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--violet) 0%, #2a1540 50%, var(--teal) 100%);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .success-page::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 50%, rgba(24, 185, 216, 0.1) 0%, transparent 60%);
        }

        .success-icon {
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--cyan), var(--teal));
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            animation: scaleIn 0.6s var(--ease-spring) 0.3s both;
        }

        .success-icon::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            inset: -8px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 2px solid rgba(24, 185, 216, 0.3);
            animation: pulseRing 2s ease-out infinite;
        }

        .success-icon::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            inset: -16px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 1px solid rgba(24, 185, 216, 0.15);
            animation: pulseRing 2s ease-out 0.5s infinite;
        }

        .success-icon svg {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            color: var(--white);
            stroke-width: 3;
        }

        .success-page h1 {
            font-family: var(--font-display);
            font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4rem);
            font-weight: 300;
            color: var(--white);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            letter-spacing: -0.02em;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s var(--ease-out) 0.6s both;
        }

        .success-page .subtitle {
            font-family: var(--font-display);
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            font-style: italic;
            font-weight: 300;
            color: var(--cyan);
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s var(--ease-out) 0.8s both;
        }

        .success-page .message {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
            max-width: 500px;
            line-height: 1.8;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s var(--ease-out) 1s both;
        }

        .success-details {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 2rem 3rem;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s var(--ease-out) 1.2s both;
        }

        .success-details p {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .success-details .label {
            color: var(--cyan);
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.1em;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
        }

        .success-quote {
            font-family: var(--font-display);
            font-style: italic;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
            max-width: 400px;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s var(--ease-out) 1.4s both;
        }

        .success-actions {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s var(--ease-out) 1.6s both;
        }

        @keyframes scaleIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: scale(0.5);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: scale(1);
            }
        }

        @keyframes pulseRing {
            0% {
                transform: scale(1);
                opacity: 1;
            }
            100% {
                transform: scale(1.5);
                opacity: 0;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .success-page {
                padding: 6rem 1.5rem 3rem;
            }
            
            .success-details {
                padding: 1.5rem;
                width: 100%;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('../partials/header') %>

    <main class="success-page">
        <div class="success-icon">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
            </svg>
        </div>

        <h1>Your Enquiry Has Landed</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">Thank you, <%= name %></p>
        
        <p class="message">
            We have received your interest in <strong style="color: var(--cyan);"><%= service %></strong>. 
            One of our team will reach out within 24 hours to begin the conversation.
        </p>

        <div class="success-details">
            <p><span class="label">What happens next</span></p>
            <p>• We review your enquiry within 24 hours</p>
            <p>• A Mindset.i representative will contact you</p>
            <p>• We schedule a brief discovery call</p>
            <p>• Together, we design the session that serves you best</p>
        </div>

        <p class="success-quote">
            "You cannot pour from an empty cup — but yours was never empty to begin with."
        </p>

        <div class="success-actions">
            <a href="/services" class="btn-primary">Explore More Services</a>
            <a href="/" class="btn-secondary">Return Home</a>
        </div>
    </main>

    <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>